Share a Single Macro in Salesforce Classic

Available in: Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
To view macros: Read on macros
To share macros: Create AND Edit on macros

Open the Macros widget. Select the macro to share. Click .

Click Sharing. Click Add. Search for a public group or user by name.
Share the macro by selecting a group or user from the Available list and clicking Add.
Set the Access Level to Read Only or Read/Write.
Click Save.
